Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.90,0:22:08.43,Shiro,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, dnes jsem...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.94,0:22:10.89,Shiro,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Promiň, zase ti zavolám.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:11.84,Shiro,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki!
